snippet.title: Duel of Summoners OFFICIAL Trailer!
snippet.description:
Duel of Summoners is an upcoming trading card game based on Mabinogi lore!  New fans and current fans are invited to play the game on Steam, September 26th!  

The OFFICIAL trailer for Duel of Summoners!  We're running a contest until 10/5/2017 called Share the Trailer!  Check our Steam page for rules and you could win a starter pack!  http://steamcommunity.com/games/duelofsummoners/announcements/detail/1467468367600922563

You can follow us on social media at the following!
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/DuelofSummoners
Twitter: https://twitter.com/DuelofSummoners
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/duelofsummoners/
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/DuelOfSummoners/
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/duelofsummoners

Of course you can also wishlist the game & follow at: http://store.steampowered.com/app/688430/Duel_of_Summoners_The_Mabinogi_Trading_Card_Game/
